Provides:	yast2-config-bootfloppy yast2-config-lilo yast2-config-bootloader
Obsoletes:	yast2-config-bootfloppy yast2-config-lilo yast2-config-bootloader
Provides:	yast2-agent-liloconf yast2-agent-prom yast2-trans-bootfloppy
